               <msContents>
                  <summary/> 
              
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <title type="complete" xml:lang="gez" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1941Mashaf">ንቅድም፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ንጽሐፍ፡
              ምጽሐፈ፡ ልደታ፡ ለማርያም፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ፡ ቅድስት፡ ጸሎታ፡ ወስእለታ፡ ያሃሉ፡ ምስሌነ፡ አሜን።</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወሀሎ፡ አሐዱ፡ ብእሲ፡ እምዐሠርቱ፡ ወክልኤቱ፡ ነገደ፡ እስራኤል፡ ዘስሙ፡ ኢዮአቄም፡
              ዘእምትዝምደ፡ ዳዊት፡ ወባዕል፡ ውእቱ፡ ፈድፋደ፡ ወሶበ፡ ያበውኡ፡ መሥዋዕተ፡ ለእግዚኣብሔር፡ ይገብር፡ ምክዕቢተ፡
              ወአልቦ፡ ዘይገብር፡ ከማሁ፡ እምደቂቀ፡ እስራኤል፡ እንዘ፡ ይኄሊ፡ ወይብል፡ ትኩን፡ መስዋዕትየ፡ ዛቲ፡ በእንተ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ 
              ደቂቀ፡ እስራኤል፡ ከመ፡ ይስረይ፡ እግዚኣብሔር፡ ኵሎ፡
              ኀጢአቶሙ። ወሶበ፡ ኮነ፡ በዐሎሙ፡ ለአይሁድ፡ አቅረቡ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ ደቂቀ፡ እስራኤል፡ መሥዋዕቶሙ። ወመጽአ፡ ብእሲ፡ እምደቂቀ፡
              እስራኤል፡ ዘስሙ፡ ሮቤል፡ ወይቤሎ፡ ለኢዮአቄም፡ ኢመፍትው፡ ለከ፡ ትቅርብ፡ ቀድሚነ፡ እስመ፡ አልብከ፡ ዘርአ፡ በውስተ፡
              እስራኤል። ወሰሚዖ፡ ኢዮአቄም፡ ዘንተ፡ ነገረ፡ ሐዘነ፡</incipit>
                     <note>See also <ref target="#a2"/>.</note>
                     <note>This manuscript's text does not entirely agree with any of the Greek, Syriac, Latin or 
                Arabic versions. 
                It is generally more concise than the Greek text and some passages are
              completely different from the Greek.
              </note>
                  </msItem>
            
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="25r" facs="f55"/>
                     <title type="complete" xml:lang="gez" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1928Mashaf">ክርስቶስ፡ አምላኪየ፡ 
                  <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe"/>ዝውእቱ፡ ዜናሃ፡ ለቅድስት፡ ወንጽሕት፡
                ማርያም፡ እሙ፡ ለክርስቶስ፡ አምላክነ፡ ወፍልሰታ፡ እምዝ፡ ዓለም፡ ውስተ፡ ሕይወት።</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወእምዝ፡ በሠለስቱ፡ ዕለት፡ ጊዜ፡ ቀትር፡ ወፅአት፡ ማርያም፡ እምቤታ፡ ወሖረት፡ ትጸሊ፡ ኀበ፡ መቀብረ፡ ወልዳ፡
                እስመ፡ ከመዝ፡ ውእቱ፡ ልማዳ፡</incipit>
                     <note>See also <ref target="#a3"/>.</note>
                     <note>This manuscript's text generally agrees with the karshuni BnF Syriaque 232,
                  <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/R9N2AUUU"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Zotenberg1874Catalogue"/><title level="m">Catalogues des manuscrits syriaques et sabéens (mandaïtes) de la Bibliothèque nationale</title><title level="s">Manuscrits orientaux</title><author><forename>Hermann</forename><surname>Zotenberg</surname></author><pubPlace>Paris</pubPlace><publisher>Imprimerie nationale</publisher><date>1874</date><series><title level="s">Manuscrits orientaux</title></series><note type="url">http://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/bpt6k2299742/f1.image</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Syriac</note><note type="tag">Catalogue</note><note type="tag">Bibliothèque Nationale</note><note type="tag">bm:Zotenberg1874Catalogue</note></note><note type="tag">Syriac</note><note type="tag">Catalogue</note><note type="tag">Bibliothèque Nationale</note><note type="tag">bm:Zotenberg1874Catalogue</note><citedRange unit="page">181</citedRange></bibl>, and the
                  Arabic edition, <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/4C56NNBN"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Enger1856Transitu"/><title level="m">Ioannis Apostoli de transitu beatae Mariae Virginis liber</title><author><forename>Maximilian</forename><surname>Enger</surname></author><pubPlace>Elberfeldae</pubPlace><publisher>R. L. Fridericus</publisher><date>1854</date><note type="url">https://archive.org/details/enger_Ioannis_apostoli_de_transitu_beatae_Mariae</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Arabic</note><note type="tag">Apocrypha</note><note type="tag">bm:Enger1856Transitu</note></note><note type="tag">Arabic</note><note type="tag">Apocrypha</note><note type="tag">bm:Enger1856Transitu</note></bibl>.
                   </note>
                  </msItem>
                  
