         <div type="edition">
            <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Fel1" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet53#ms_i2">
               <ab>
                  <note>The following is the passage on the apostles' reunion following the Holy Spirit's announcement
